<paragraph id="7D6C4D07A71BD6CBD5A46421B099688D" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Weicher Storchschnabel</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="FB57417B54AE2F244E326ED72C6FEC07" pageId="null" pageNumber="621" type="description">
<paragraph id="18FB2172F78D69DB4A2B83C84889D023" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="04F6FE745BF74BF3BF85E83FD3E57C93" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Geranium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="621" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pusillum">
<emphasis id="7D355D9EF5FEE8BD71749EBCF72892C2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">G. pusillum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 6) durch folgende Merkmale: Stengel abstehend behaart (
<emphasis id="C5094350B02B43269317430B3D1C0A7A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
Haare sehr 
<normalizedToken id="706E527DCA69C8D6D60A5D4A8785BB5A" originalValue="dünn" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">duenn</normalizedToken>
, 1-2 mm lang
</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="B1DA11DD0DB26B0BBF09FE26C274240A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
; 
<normalizedToken id="5B56CB3DEE33E57191CEBCD9915E90A6" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
am Stengel meist 
<normalizedToken id="6EB5E3B1F2E7D75944D3FDA082A3D9D9" originalValue="wechselständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">wechselstaendig</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, bis auf etwa 
<normalizedToken id="EC22FD76DEE2B00AB4A7BDB48F5DD67D" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">1/2</normalizedToken>
5-9teilig; Zipfel und 
<normalizedToken id="896DAEA7A5BB131EBDF2FFF8CE7F41DF" originalValue="Zähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Zaehne</normalizedToken>
1- 
<normalizedToken id="1FB11A3729E84617FC6A5BFD4BB848E7" originalValue="1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie breit; 
<normalizedToken id="E85C42BC20E56CA8AC451EF5E3A028C8" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
und Kelch mit 0,1-0,2 mm langen 
<normalizedToken id="159F80FC3E80D55B92F2E4BEE01349F9" originalValue="Drüsenhaaren" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Druesenhaaren</normalizedToken>
und 
<emphasis id="EDD02259F5AB5C83E3238D2DD0D20A95" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
sehr 
<normalizedToken id="5450D581B29FF7BEC770F824C5C1FB72" originalValue="dünnen" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">duennen</normalizedToken>
, 1-2 mm langen, abstehenden Haaren;
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="95ED35FA6F3FD0649E230135A162AB7B" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
3-5 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="61EA7980E7FCEFA3F7EDC9D8B35D3D22" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
4-6 mm lang, rosa; 
<emphasis id="1407FC3C84AE63311A9A7F692C3BEA06" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Frucht im untern</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="D74C2B503E25EDCB2001708144A7490B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">verdickten</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="B46B174B6661CAF6C8C7736023D0A386" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Teil mit zahlreichen Querfalten, kahl</emphasis>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="51EECA673EB3C9AEC1B95569A9C6E64E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="079E58BBB43C05F169BE4A0243EAC3B7" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="E9BE82BF7088D5691DBE1542DAD46BDA" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
, Sommer und Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9C14ACBFA9410F93AEF9FD44BA3AD8B3" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
<emphasis id="0FE8E027BF27B623EF9F63150CC10BE0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="CB5485C7C9D8269030AA428326C9C427" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">26:</emphasis>
Material aus Schleswig-Holstein (Gauger 1937), aus England (Warburg 1938), aus Island (
<normalizedToken id="FBA08A6DA31A69FC235ABE50648C2103" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="5F92A980E19CECECCFB84C88D13862CD" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1956b), aus 
<normalizedToken id="09CFAB717874E47D39180CFC25C9765C" originalValue="Dänemark" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Daenemark</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="16C480385DC7EB10D875522CEFD44326" originalValue="Böcher" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Boecher</normalizedToken>
und Larsen 1958), aus Kanada (Mulligan 1959), aus Holland (Gadella und Kliphuis 1966).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B4C04021B061EA914C1A6B12D985C332" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
<emphasis id="481F47AC512C3EE07B054AA51D81C47A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Standort</emphasis>
. Kollin und montan. Trockene, lockere, stickstoffreiche 
<normalizedToken id="08BED54CCACC16FAF1DBBFFC2A76D37D" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="3113CA2FAECA7FDA6E7B90725B763721" originalValue="wärmeren" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">waermeren</normalizedToken>
Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="BAA3716B451930526668EB2F73811630" originalValue="Wegränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Wegraender</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="AEB27B3E87E82131D3AB5BEE3BCAD706" originalValue="Äcker" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Aecker</normalizedToken>
, um 
<normalizedToken id="455FAC3AEAF2398BBAE698F43D988A3F" originalValue="Häuser" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Haeuser</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="68941A775AD7DAF4ACAA468611E0B978" originalValue="Lägerstellen" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Laegerstellen</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B3723547362AE5F7FB56104F29E74374" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">
<emphasis id="B2273DEEBF37E3337E0B479145990739" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Verbreitung</emphasis>
. 
<normalizedToken id="F9564A59AAB259CC80838B080556FFF9" originalValue="Ursprünglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">Urspruenglich</normalizedToken>
wahrscheinlich 
<emphasis id="A77864EBFCD8002CEECADBD326661BD1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">mediterrane Pflanze;</emphasis>
heute 
<normalizedToken id="05E5DEC05BA36039E32CE8E0026087B7" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">ueber</normalizedToken>
weite Gebiete der Erde verbreitet. - Im Gebiet ziemlich verbreitet, nicht 
<normalizedToken id="4A6D740E5A2EBC7C7BE84899DB246329" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="621">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
